{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2016/04/ra-mat-nodejs-v6.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ce1fc69d-446a-55dd-81a6-3d334b712518","html":"<p>Hôm nay 26/04, Node.js vừa ra mắt <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/blog/release/v6.0.0/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">phiên bản v6.0.0</a>, với nhiều cải tiến về hiệu suất, load module nhanh hơn đáng kể, cải tiến Buffer, File System APIs, tests và tài liệu tốt hơn.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.duyet.net/2016/04/ra-mat-nodejs-v6.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_fNbLVO5xXM/VyDN2wT51fI/AAAAAAAAT7o/XeHb_vlbC4AM85F9_UpRHBJhOhT0a2wNwCK4B/s640/Node-dot-js-796x398.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p>Nodejs v6.0.0 sử dụng V8 JavaScript engine, giúp hỗ trợ hơn 93% các <a href=\"https://blog.duyet.net/2016/04/es6.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">chức năng mới trong ES6</a>. Hiệu tại Nodejs v6 được công bố là “Current Release”, tức là bạn đã có thể nâng cấp lên Nodejs ngay thời điểm này.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>New “Current” version line focuses on performance improvements, increased reliability and better security for its 3.5 million users - <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/blog/announcements/v6-release/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://nodejs.org/en/blog/announcements/v6-release/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Các điểm mới trong Nodejs v6:</p>\n<h2 id=\"nâng-cấp-hiệu-năng\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#n%C3%A2ng-c%E1%BA%A5p-hi%E1%BB%87u-n%C4%83ng\" aria-label=\"nâng cấp hiệu năng permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Nâng cấp hiệu năng</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Load module nhanh hơn gấp 4 lần so với Nodejs v4</li>\n<li>Nâng cấp V8 engine</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"bảo-mật\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#b%E1%BA%A3o-m%E1%BA%ADt\" aria-label=\"bảo mật permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bảo mật</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Math.random</code> được tăng cường bảo mật, xem thêm: <a href=\"http://v8project.blogspot.hu/2015/12/theres-mathrandom-and-then-theres.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://v8project.blogspot.hu/2015/12/theres-mathrandom-and-then-theres.html</a></li>\n<li>Buffer API mới: giảm khả năng lỗi và lỗ hổng cho ứng dụng.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"es6-features\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#es6-features\" aria-label=\"es6 features permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ES6 Features</h2>\n<p>Như đã nói ở trên, Nodejs v6 hỗ trợ 93% các chức năng mới của ES6 mà không cần dùng compile Babel như trước đây.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">var x = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]  \nvar [y, z] = x  \nconsole.log(y) // 1  \nconsole.log(z) // 2</code></pre></div>\n<p>Xem thêm <a href=\"https://blog.duyet.net/2016/04/es6.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ES6 có gì mới?</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"nâng-cấp-lên-nodejs-v6\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#n%C3%A2ng-c%E1%BA%A5p-l%C3%AAn-nodejs-v6\" aria-label=\"nâng cấp lên nodejs v6 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Nâng cấp lên Nodejs v6</h2>\n<p>Sử dụng nvm:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">nvm install 6</code></pre></div>\n<p>Trường hợp không sử dụng nvm:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo npm install -g n # Cài n\nsudo n latest # Install or activate the latest node release</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"tham-khảo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tham-kh%E1%BA%A3o\" aria-label=\"tham khảo permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tham khảo</h2>\n<p>Tháng 10 năm nay Nodejs v6 mới chính thức chuyển sang phiên bản TLS. </p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.risingstack.com/whats-new-in-node-v6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://blog.risingstack.com/whats-new-in-node-v6/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/blog/release/v6.0.0/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://nodejs.org/en/blog/release/v6.0.0/</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/2016/04/ra-mat-nodejs-v6.html","tagSlugs":["/tag/nodejs/","/tag/release/","/tag/node-js/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2016-04-27T21:54:00.001+07:00","description":"Ra mắt Node.js v6.0.0","tags":["Nodejs","release","Node.js"],"title":"Ra mắt Node.js v6.0.0","fbCommentUrl":"none"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2016/04/ra-mat-nodejs-v6.html"}}}